title: Match of the Day 2 - 3rd May 2015 - hdtv x264
description:
SPORT: Match of the Day 2
On: BBC 1 HD
Date: Sunday 3rd May 2015
Time: 22:30 to 23:35

Mark Chapman introduces highlights from the day's two Premier League fixtures. Chelsea have dominated the top flight for much of the season, and the Blues begin the final month of the campaign with a London derby against Crystal Palace. The day's other game also comes from the capital, with champions Manchester City visiting Tottenham Hotspur. City have scored 15 goals in their past three meetings with Spurs, conceding just two - will there be another sky blue goal glut at White Hart Lane? There is also a chance to see all the goals from Saturday's top-flight games.
